data.description: Discover the potential in this 4-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home, nestled in the heart of Newport News. With a generous 3,307 square feet, this property is a blank canvas waiting for your personal touch. An excellent opportunity for investors or home renovators looking for their next project to turn this diamond in the rough into your dream home. Great for large families or multi-generational living, this spacious residence provides room for everyone to spread out and find their own space. Imagine the memories you'll create while putting your own stamp on this home. Call today to schedule a viewing! Property to be sold “as-is, where is”.
